headline: The Lone Star State — and Trump — versus BlackRock
summary: The US Justice Department and the FTC is siding with Texas Attorney General Ken Paxton and 12 other Republican-led states in an antitrust case against trillion-dollar asset managers BlackRock (BLK) and its rivals State Street and Vanguard. The charge: a left-wing ideological attack on coal.
